Megatron smiled a broad smile, he knew what kind of service he had 
just gotten, "Excellent, I know I can expect a lot from you. How much 
more time untill we reach our destination?" he asked.


On the ground, the Stunticons were reaching the water. Motormaster 
stopped, skidding towards the cliff of the ocean. As Wildrider and 
Speedbreaker fluidly roared of the cliff, and transformed still 
flying, he opened his trailor compartment. "Can you fly?" he asked 
harshly, and furiously to Symphony.
